These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, tennis, skiing
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, brown, apricot, turquise
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | baseball | basketball | skiing | tennis |
| Color        | coral | brown   | turquise | apricot    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different games are played: go, domino, monopoly, canasta
House: modern, colonial, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
4. the modern house is the person playing go##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the modern house is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Game   | monopoly | go  | domino  | canasta |
| House   | ranch-style    | modern | cape-cod | colonial    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: go, domino, billiard, canasta
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, emerald, apricot, red
1. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Game          | canasta | billiard | domino    | go      |
| Color   | apricot        | red     | black | emerald |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, australian, thai
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, romance, mystery, disaster
1. the polish is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
2. the thai is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality         | thai | japanese | polish | australian |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | crime   | romance    | disaster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
House: art-deco, townhouse, modern, craftsman
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
1. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the craftsman house##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
5. the modern house is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| House   | townhouse  | art-deco    | modern   | craftsman       |
| Hobby   | traveling | sudoku | reading | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, september, october
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, basketball, golf, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | september      | february | october | march |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball     | cycling  | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, balloon-flower, tulip
House: futuristic, wooden, tower, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
2. the tower house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the art-deco house is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
6. the wooden house is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | daffodil | tulip | balloon-flower | bellflower    |
| House     | art-deco | tower  | futuristic     | wooden |

