.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, june, october
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, mirinda, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person drinking mirinda##2
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Birthday   | december | march      | october | june |
| Beverage   | milk  | juice | 7up    | mirinda            |

