.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, funk, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skiing, lacrosse, climbing
1. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is skiing and the fan of funk##2
4. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | metal   | ambient | funk |
| Sport    | climbing     | skiing | cycling     | lacrosse  |

