.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, sunflower, lily
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, adventure, crime
1. the person who growsrose is the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person who growssunflower##2
4. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Flower      | dahlia       | sunflower   | rose | lily |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | disaster | crime        | satire    |

