4. the lily-polo house is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | begonia   | lily   | daffodil      | rose      |
| House      | futuristic | modern | lily-polo | colonial |

