.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, baking, video-games, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, handball, swimming, sailing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | drawing | baking  | video-games  | dancing |
| Sport   | sailing  | swimming | parkour | handball   |

