.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
City: rome, paris, nizza, boston
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, dog, goat
1. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
4. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| City   | paris | rome | nizza | boston  |
| Pet     | fish   | chinchilla  | goat  | dog |

