.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, lacrosse, swimming
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, nurse, firefighter, paramedic
1. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the lawyer is on the right of the paramedic##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the lawyer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Sport   | lacrosse | swimming | skiing | cricket |
| Job           | paramedic     | lawyer     | firefighter   | nurse         |

