.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, house, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, polish, argentine, dutch
1. the fan of d&b is between the russian and the fan of folk##2
2. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the dutch is in an odd position##4
6. the argentine is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Music-Genre   | pop | folk         | d&b   | house |
| Nationality   | argentine    | polish | dutch | russian   |

