.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
House: palace, colonial, cape-cod, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, baccarat, siglo, havana
1. the havana-smoker is the cape-cod house##1
2. the siglo-smoker is the palace house##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
5. the palace house is in an even position##4
6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| House   | colonial | palace | cape-cod    | farmhouse |
| Cigar   | alhambra   | siglo  | havana | baccarat     |

