.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
City: marseilles, hannover, london, new-york
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, classical, dubstep
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
3. the fan of ambient is the person traveling to london##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| City         | new-york   | london | marseilles | hannover    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | ambient  | dubstep     | reggae |

