.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, pink, lilac, fuchsia
House: modern, cape-cod, gothic-revival, art-deco
1. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
7. the modern house is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Color   | fuchsia | orange    | lilac       | pink |
| House       | cape-cod  | gothic-revival | art-deco | modern  |

