.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, snowboarding, handball
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | sprite | cola  | tea |
| Sport     | rowing      | snowboarding       | badminton | handball     |

