.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, whist, domino
City: miami, rome, new-york, san-francisco
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
3. the person traveling to rome is between the person playing poker and the person traveling to miami##2
4. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Game         | poker | whist   | domino | canasta |
| City   | san-francisco          | rome | miami         | new-york  |

 